{"tid":1485662,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"作為一個和理非，多謝前線今日的合作","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:28:58.000Z","uid":230703,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"25cc28908c4812b760695c9a30fdb40449c86a6d","tid":1485662,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"作為一個和理非，多謝前線今日的合作<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地。大家輪換，互相合作，堅持落去。<br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"e680fee3f83520ced6758b61e2f5546fe5904f13","tid":1485662,"uid":266683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nO7z36x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnO7z36x.jpg&h=5563f555&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e9367ab2494e012307565f4587d692b1337b089","tid":1485662,"uid":182827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"多謝今日咁多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bb5fa98bf58e8016f2eccf0a16b12db29a23bd","tid":1485662,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"腳都斷 但值得 多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3b2d8eae6a0b18f948d867273ce84c683b206f","tid":1485662,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:05.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"e94786aa8e786dd7b6a0bdc89a96b11771be5c5c","tid":1485662,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"真係多謝佢地合作， 大家要齊上齊落。<br />\n<br />\n方法可能唔同。但目標一致"},{"pid":"99541de74fb5c3268575b1b4a8063ff8b91d9f65","tid":1485662,"uid":2517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"多謝前線手足"},{"pid":"e5d7d29f75f1a85587c55f89c10af0e1644282a2","tid":1485662,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"多謝前線手足"},{"pid":"7b4d81b908dbed03093ac6f9ce8c08d748c21ec7","tid":1485662,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"多謝肯回家休息的前線"},{"pid":"d96ef1d91b4bc4ba70c0317ba37f219af5f168ce","tid":1485662,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b4d81b908dbed03093ac6f9ce8c08d748c21ec7","tid":1485662,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"多謝肯回家休息的前線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"對，多謝"},{"pid":"09a6355f562001df1495d20871fb395ce5f01b7d","tid":1485662,"uid":13874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"多謝大家合作"},{"pid":"02de77a113fa78d54bfb65ffd3b2288c0049141d","tid":1485662,"uid":122122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6e74435bf2cf4c7c673eb91ad4142abd871aae","tid":1485662,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<strong>解放軍係10分鐘之內就可以落黎香港<br />\n美國可以一夜之間取消香港關係法<br />\n隨便一樣野都足以致命<br />\n令所有外資撤退，港元急速貶值</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"38c7a04413dfbe352e64fa668082a5eed122a1e7","tid":1485662,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"［永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進］今日總結，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485890</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成（搶佔國際輿論），冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得可能唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同時之間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，加上客觀因素（現場人多電話收到嘅信號會少/ 局勢變化可能太快）散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度，兵荒馬亂之際大家嘅心情難免心急，語氣上亦會有所失儀，唯希望大家之後仍然可以再度團結，齊上齊落，打贏呢一場逆權運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185a85cc8c3812b75103f393298fcf0d8c9bdbe8","tid":1485662,"uid":52076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"多謝每一個為香港前途企出黎既同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}